msgstr ""

#. [unit]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:126
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1213
